---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Why Lumphammer?"
  description="The origin story of the Lumphammer name, inspired by a classic Red Dwarf episode."
>
  <main class="container">
    <h1>
      Why <mark>&quot;Lumphammer&quot;</mark>?
    </h1>
    <p>
      &ldquo;The accident involving me, the toaster, the waste disposal, and a
      fourteen pound <mark>lumphammer</mark>.&rdquo;
    </p>
    <p>
      <iframe
        style={{
          width: "100%",
          maxWidth: "800px",
          aspectRatio: "4 / 3",
        }}
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LRq_SAuQDec?si=MxoWdknBrdpMD718"
        title="YouTube video player"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        referrer-policy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
        allow-full-screen></iframe>
    </p>
    <p>
      That&apos;s why. I was watching this episode of{" "}
      <a target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Dwarf">
        Red Dwarf
      </a>{" "}
      late one night and it just tickled me so I ran over to the computer and registered
      the name.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
